00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:30,920
Not necessarily.

573
00:27:35,800 --> 00:27:36,400
This blind man

574
00:27:36,479 --> 00:27:37,479
hides his true martial arts skills.

575
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:39,160
It's a bit difficult for me to handle him alone.

576
00:27:39,319 --> 00:27:40,280
Three against one is more worthwhile.

577
00:27:40,319 --> 00:27:41,359
You're already at a disadvantage.

578
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:43,400
I gave your medicine to Linlang.

579
00:27:45,359 --> 00:27:46,520
It's not a loss for her to take it.

580
00:27:47,280 --> 00:27:48,000
Lu Jiu

581
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:49,199
Hurry and take Linlang away.

582
00:27:49,239 --> 00:27:50,079
Leave this to me.

583
00:27:50,199 --> 00:27:51,319
Enough talk.

584
00:28:11,520 --> 00:28:12,319
Lu Jiu

585
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:20,920
Lu Jiu

586
00:28:20,959 --> 00:28:22,000
Quick, take Linlang away.

587
00:28:22,119 --> 00:28:22,839
Go!

588
00:28:28,479 --> 00:28:30,119
We can't leave Sima Kong alone.

589
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:31,359
I know.

590
00:28:35,560 --> 00:28:37,319
Lu Jiu, don't do anything foolish.

591
00:28:37,800 --> 00:28:39,560
Letting the ones you care about escape danger

592
00:28:40,280 --> 00:28:41,400
isn't foolish.

593
00:28:42,719 --> 00:28:43,599
You said before

594
00:28:43,599 --> 00:28:45,359
that for my sake, you would take care of yourself.

595
00:28:45,959 --> 00:28:46,760
Lu Jiu

596
00:28:47,280 --> 00:28:48,439
Let me make a bet with you.

597
00:28:49,199 --> 00:28:50,160
If I win,

598
00:28:51,800 --> 00:28:53,680
you'll treat me to candied hawthorn for a lifetime.

599
00:28:58,920 --> 00:29:00,040
Lu Jiu

600
00:29:05,800 --> 00:29:06,959
If I lose,

601
00:29:07,800 --> 00:29:09,319
I just hope you can remember

602
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:12,119
that there was once someone named Lu Jiu

603
00:29:13,280 --> 00:29:15,040
who appeared in your life.

604
00:29:23,880 --> 00:29:25,199
Want to die?

605
00:29:26,199 --> 00:29:27,400
I'll help you on your way.

606
00:29:27,439 --> 00:29:28,160
Stop!

607
00:29:33,760 --> 00:29:34,719
You want to kill him.

608
00:29:34,839 --> 00:29:35,880
But have you asked me?

609
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:36,959
Why did you come back?

610
00:29:37,119 --> 00:29:38,239
Even when beating a dog, you have to consider its master.

611
00:29:38,319 --> 00:29:39,079
You work for me.

612
00:29:39,119 --> 00:29:40,400
If he bullies you, isn't he bullying me too?

613
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:42,959
You're the real dog here.

614
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:46,040
Even with one more person,

615
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:47,680
you're still no match for me.

616
00:29:47,760 --> 00:29:49,199
Who said there's only one more?

617
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:51,959
I'm here too.

618
00:29:55,280 --> 00:29:57,280
You actually came back on your own.

619
00:29:57,479 --> 00:29:58,400
That nine-linked lock,

620
00:29:58,520 --> 00:29:59,760
isn't it impossible to open from the outside?

621
00:29:59,800 --> 00:30:01,439
Did you forget? I'm incredibly strong.

622
00:30:01,560 --> 00:30:02,479
The door you couldn't blow open,

623
00:30:02,520 --> 00:30:03,880
I took it apart easily.

624
00:30:04,040 --> 00:30:05,119
You two idiots.

625
00:30:05,280 --> 00:30:06,319
I've been struggling to hold on here.

626
00:30:06,359 --> 00:30:07,959
It's not so you two could come back and get yourselves killed.

627
00:30:08,319 --> 00:30:09,239
Enough talking.

628
00:30:09,319 --> 00:30:11,119
Let's hurry up and bring Li Mu to justice.

629
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:14,800
Just the three of you?

630
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:16,239
You really overestimate yourselves.

631
00:30:41,959 --> 00:30:42,800
Lu Jiu.

632
00:31:01,760 --> 00:31:02,719
I understand now.

633
00:31:02,920 --> 00:31:04,719
He's in a hurry to swap my face with the corpse's.

634
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:05,800
It's because the corpse

635
00:31:05,839 --> 00:31:06,959
won't last much longer.

636
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:08,319
Then let's stall for time.

637
00:31:08,560 --> 00:31:09,280
This way,

638
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:11,239
his evil plan won't succeed.

639
00:31:20,959 --> 00:31:21,719
Linlang.

640
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:22,880
Linlang.

641
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:29,439
Are you okay?
